<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Well, this weapon has gotten much better now that it does not stack with the shaman and enchanter spells since last patch. This is one of the best weapons a rogue can get now because of being able to use the proc even if shaman and enchanters cast the spell. </font></td></tr></table>
