<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>A few of you seem to have it backwards, the proc does not slow YOU down, but rather the mob.  The reason people used to call this a drawback was becauese of a bug that made weak slow spells like this one overwrite good slow spells like togor's and turgur's.  The bug has been fixed... this weapon rocks now.<BR>
<BR>
-Gikk, 48 shaman<BR>
